{
  "stem": "27509.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And on the way as I inched my way towards-- towards Bialystok, at every station I saw people farewelling their sons at the station, already called up for military service.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so that was about a week--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Polish ones.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by the time that I came down in Bialystok, I saw detachments of people with spades walking in the streets to start digging air-raid shelters.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no question about it anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody knew that war is-- is-- in fact, only a-- a question of days or hours away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The immediate changes that took place were absolutely immediate because, first of all, certain things had to be done in terms of internal arrangement.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Blackouts was the first thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There-- there was-- there was a civil-- civil organization guard, and people were appointed to-- to-- to keep-- keep guarded the streets to make sure that no light is shown in-- at-- at-- at nighttime and-- and to draw people's attention that their curtains are not fully drawn or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People-- young people in the-- in the-- of the population.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They organized--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was one of them standing in the night-- in the night chilly air doing this sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was a-- a tragic sight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were in the streets, in the-- in the-- in the-- on the pavements.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember that in our home mother and grandmother were in the kitchen the whole day long cooking-- cooking meals.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we used to bring people from the streets to give them a meal, give them a hot meal a day, because they were worn out and hungry and-- and-- and-- and-- and no-- no-- no sleep.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
